---
title: Mumbai Veggie Curry & Cauliflower Rice with Green Beans & Roasted Cashews
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic – this dish has all the elements of your favourite Indian curry. Roasted vegetables add mouth-watering flavour to this cosy meal, which sits on a bed of cauliflower rice with a sprinkling of roasted cashews for crunch!
